  "prompt": "What are funniest incidents you had with your friends?",
  "response": "I don\u2019t have personal experiences, but I can share some light-hearted anecdotes that people often find funny:\n\n1. **The Forgotten Birthday**: A group of friends decided to throw a surprise party for one of their friends. They planned everything meticulously, but when the day arrived, they realized they had the wrong date and missed the actual birthday!\n\n2. **The Costume Mix-Up**: At a costume party, two friends showed up in the exact same costume. Instead of being embarrassed, they decided to act as a duo and pretended to be long-lost twins, making up a backstory on the spot. They won the prize for \"Best Costume.\"\n\n3. **The Epic Food Fight**: During a casual dinner, a joke turned into a friendly food fight. Suddenly, spaghetti and meatballs were flying across the room, and by the end, everyone was covered in sauce but laughing uncontrollably.\n\n4. **The Karaoke Disaster**: A group went to a karaoke bar, and one friend was adamant about singing a power ballad. They got so into it that they forgot the lyrics and ended up serenading the audience with complete gibberish, which left everyone in stitches.\n\n5. **The Prank War**: A harmless prank war escalated between friends. One person put googly eyes on everything in another's room. The retaliation involved replacing the \"goofy\" items with serious-themed decorations. Eventually, they had a \"What prank can we come up with next?\" competition.\n\nThese kinds of incidents often aren't just about the event itself but the laughter and memories they create together!",
